languages.text: "Мы также засекли скопление космического мусора в районе станционных доков. Предположительно — осколки межпланетарных шаттлов. Возможно, многоуважаемый дом Навис Нобилите нуждается в помощи... И потому не может ответить на вокс-передачу".

languages.text: "We have also detected an accumulation of space debris near the station's docks. Presumably, it is the remains of interplanetary shuttles. Perhaps the esteemed Navis Nobilite House requires aid... and therefore, cannot respond to our vox-transmission."

languages.text: « Nous avons également détecté un amoncellement de débris à proximité des quais de la station. Selon toute vraisemblance, il s'agit d'épaves de navettes interplanétaires. Il est possible que l'illustre maison de la Navis Nobilite ait besoin d'assistance... Voilà qui pourrait expliquer son silence-vox, en tout cas. »

languages.text: "Wir haben zudem in der Nähe der Docks der Station eine Ansammlung von Raumschutt lokalisiert. Mutmaßlich sind das die Überreste interplanetarer Shuttles. Vielleicht benötigt das ehrwürdige Haus Navis Nobilite Hilfe ... Und kann daher nicht auf unsere Vox-Übertragung antworten."
languages.original_text: "We have also detected an accumulation of space debris near the station's docks. Presumably, it is the remains of interplanetary shuttles. Perhaps the esteemed Navis Nobilite House requires aid... and therefore, cannot respond to our vox-transmission."

languages.text: «También hemos detectado una acumulación de restos espaciales cerca de los muelles de la estación. Por lo visto, son escombros de lanzaderas interplanetarias. Es posible que la venerable Navis Nobilite necesite ayuda... Y sería la razón por la que no responden a nuestra transmisión de voco».
languages.original_text: "We have also detected an accumulation of space debris near the station's docks. Presumably, it is the remains of interplanetary shuttles. Perhaps the esteemed Navis Nobilite House requires aid... and therefore, cannot respond to our vox-transmission."

languages.text: “我们还在星站船坞附近发现了大量太空碎片。据推测，这些碎片是星际穿梭机的残骸。或许尊贵的导航宗族需要援助……因此无法回应我们的音阵信息。”
languages.original_text: "We have also detected an accumulation of space debris near the station's docks. Presumably, it is the remains of interplanetary shuttles. Perhaps the esteemed Navis Nobilite House requires aid... and therefore, cannot respond to our vox-transmission."

languages.text: 「また、ステーションのドック付近に宇宙ゴミが溜まっているようです。おそらく、惑星間シャトルの残骸でしょう。ご立派な航宙貴族の一族は助けを必要としているのではないでしょうか…そのため、こちらのヴォクス通信に応答できないのかと」
languages.original_text: "We have also detected an accumulation of space debris near the station's docks. Presumably, it is the remains of interplanetary shuttles. Perhaps the esteemed Navis Nobilite House requires aid... and therefore, cannot respond to our vox-transmission."

languages.text: "Ayrıca istasyonun rıhtımlarının yakınlarında bir uzay enkazı birikimi tespit ettik. Tahminen gezegenler arası mekiklerin kalıntıları. Belki de değerli Navis Nobilite Hanesi'nin desteğe ihtiyacı vardır ve bu nedenle de voks iletilerimize yanıt veremiyordur."
languages.original_text: "We have also detected an accumulation of space debris near the station's docks. Presumably, it is the remains of interplanetary shuttles. Perhaps the esteemed Navis Nobilite House requires aid... and therefore, cannot respond to our vox-transmission."
